<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width">
  <title>Rocket Mission</title>
</head>

<body>

  <center>
    <h1>Welcome to My Rocket Mission!</h1>

    <p>Today, our rocket is getting ready to travel across space.</p>

    <h2>Step 1: Meet the Rocket</h2>
    <img src="rocket.png" alt="A rocket ready to launch" width="350" height="350">

    <p>This rocket will take us to a new planet.</p>

    <h2>Step 2: Our Space Destination</h2>
    <img src="planet.png" alt="A colourful planet in space" width="350" height="350">

    <p>We found a beautiful planet far away from Earth.</p>

    <h2>Step 3: The Space Explorer</h2>
    <img src="astronaut.png" alt="An astronaut exploring space" width="350" height="350">

    <p>The astronaut is ready to explore the planet.</p>

    <h2>Mission Complete!</h2>
    <p>We used the image tag to add pictures and tell a space story on our webpage.</p>
  </center>

</body>

</html>

