<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width">
  <title>Aquatic Beats Party</title>
</head>

<body>

  <center>

    <h1>Aquatic Beats Party</h1>

    <h2>The ocean stage is ready!</h2>

    <p>
      Play the music and watch the aquatic animals swim through their beautiful underwater world.
    </p>

    <audio controls loop>
      <source src="music.mp3" type="audio/mpeg">
      Your browser does not support the audio tag.
    </audio>

    <br><br>

    <video width="500" height="350" controls poster="poster.png" loop>
      <source src="aqua.mp4" type="video/mp4">
      Your browser does not support the video tag.
    </video>

    <h2>The ocean show is live!</h2>

    <p>
      This webpage uses the audio tag for music and the video tag to bring the aquatic animal adventure to life.
    </p>

  </center>

</body>

</html>

