<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width">
  <title>Iframe in HTML</title>
</head>

<body>

  <center>

    <h1>Super game zone</h1>

    <h2>Play the challenge inside this webpage!</h2>

    <p>
      Jump, move, dodge, and try to complete the game without opening a new tab.
    </p>

    <iframe 
      src="https://scratch.mit.edu/projects/60917032/embed"
      allowtransparency="true"
      width="500"
      height="400"
      frameborder="0"
      scrolling="no"
      allowfullscreen>
    </iframe>

    <h2>The game is live!</h2>

    <p>
      This webpage uses an iframe to show an exciting Scratch game directly inside HTML.
    </p>

  </center>

</body>

</html>
